item.description:
Calling all shutterbugs .... let's meet up somewhere around Boston/a small New England town and go trigger happy. Bring your DSLR, point-and-shoot or any other camera and let's take some awesome pictures... Members experienced in photography can guide buddying hobbyists ....
Experts can hone their skills ...
Once done, we can all meetup over lunch/dinner to critique each other's snaps
item.name: Photography and More
